      "content": "that's a good high-level start, but it's a bit vague. i need something i can actually use for our marketing segmentation. can you get more granular with the demographics? like, what does this person actually look like? give me specifics on age, ethnicity, geographic location, and maybe some details on their family or cultural background to help us tailor the visuals.",
